<h2 class="bold font-l">BB - Bad Memory and Haircut</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
In Season 8 &quot;Are You There Bob? It's Me, Birthday&quot;, Linda has forgotten Bob's birthday and Gene has bungled bangs. </p>
</div>
